::Ender::
       Ender caught the second optic blast in the chest flipping him 
backwards.  He landed on his feet and stumbled back a step.  "Now that wasn't 
very nice."  His eyes gleamed, almost demonically with a psychotic rage.  
"KEEHEEHEE!"  He launched himself into the air transforming mid-flight and 
coming down behind Rodimus Prime.  Turning around to face Rodimus Prime.  
"So, Rody, you ready to feel my wrath, eh?"  He grinned and fired a two quick 
shots at his back.

--part1_43.dd82732.2a551c3b_boundary
